#

Crispy Skin Duck Breast with Cherry Gastrique

40 min
$25
600 kcal
Difficulty: 40%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh Protein

Cuisine:

FrenchAmerican

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

DinnerEasyGourmet

Description

Tender duck breast with a crispy skin, drizzled with a sweet and tangy cherry sauce.

Ingredients

  • duck breast: 2 pieces
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • cherries (pitted and halved): 1 cup
  • sugar: 1/4 cup
  • red wine vinegar: 1/4 cup
  • chicken broth: 1/2 cup
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
